{"tid":1808150,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"裝修判頭涉嫌渠蓋襲擊途人　案件押至3月被告不准保釋","createTime":"2020-01-02T07:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T04:32:50.000Z","uid":37831,"like":19,"dislike":87,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"0c467ac6da31dda901db7aece39193cd774b811b","tid":1808150,"uid":37831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:47:44.000Z","msg":"一名男子上月1日凌晨在旺角清理路障時，懷疑被人以渠蓋襲擊，導致腦部積血以及要縫10針。一名任職裝修判頭的33歲男子在除夕夜被捕，被控一項有意圖而傷人罪，在西九龍裁判法院提堂。被告暫時毋須答辯，不准保釋，還押至3月12日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n控方形容案件「手法兇殘」，申請將案件押後，以待警方進一步調查，並為事主申請禁止報道令，不准任何人報道可識別事主身分的資料。辯方就質疑閉路電視片段中人是否被告，又指事主在片段中疑似手持棍狀物。<br />\n<br />\n主任裁判官羅德泉聽取雙方陳詞後，拒絕被告保釋申請，將案押後至3月。<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500679-20200102.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500679-20200102.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=8d131f78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500679-20200102.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c0395fa4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500679-20200102.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又唔比保釋<br />\n屌你721拉哂人未阿"},{"pid":"818fa1c2bbf3eb9906af2ef9b63265ff37012c49","tid":1808150,"uid":302,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:49:25.000Z","msg":"手法兇殘 話緊班黑警？"},{"pid":"db440cbd803dd98a83b57c1076a8e2bc47a932ae","tid":1808150,"uid":37831,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:51:05.000Z","msg":"又係紅官羅德泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc32ec9e8603a05fe5de1e2c51a5ea6e82953407","tid":1808150,"uid":37831,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:52:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-lar